// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1214 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 7d7a5a13-7bec-51dc-8405-0385a5ebba85

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
